author: kukunamuniu
title: Just a few bricks
review:
I mostly get LEGO Star Wars magazine sets to decorate my desk at work and swoosh around when nothing's happening. Of the ones I have, this one is imo the least interesting. Few parts, the wings don't block in position like in other shuttles.

Also, the wings do not protrude below the bottom of the cockpit, so it looks nothing like in the movie.
